AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GENEPIO_0001123> "PCDS: The sample ID should represent the identifier assigned to the sample at time of collection, for which all the descriptive information applies. Every sample ID from a single submitter must be unique. The ID may use any format, but should be concise, consistent within the lab, and informative where possible. If the original sample ID is unknown or cannot be provided, leave blank or provide a null value."@en)
