AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GENEPIO_0100089> "complete Kawasaki syndrome"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GENEPIO_0100089> "complete Kawasaki disease"@en)
