AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GENEPIO_0100565> "A data item which is a statement confirming that quality control processes were carried out and that the sequence did not meet the assessment criteria, however the issues detected were minor."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000118> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GENEPIO_0100565> "minor quality control issues identified"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.org/dc/terms/contributor> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GENEPIO_0100565> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1107-9135>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.org/dc/terms/contributor> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GENEPIO_0100565> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-9578-0788>)
